title: Binance axes 8 Australian Dollar trading pairs
description:
Crypto exchange Binance will remove spot trading activities for eight digital assets, including Apecoin, and Shiba Inu, paired with the Australian Dollar (AUD) on May 26. Other affected crypto assets include Chainlink (LINK), Polkadot (DOT), Axie Infinity (AXS), Avalanche (AVAX), Fantom (FTM), and Sandbox (SAND).
